      <title>中东战争风险上升 伊朗石油悄然复苏成为焦点</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-10-04/mideast-s-rising-war-risk-puts-spotlight-on-iran-s-quiet-oil-comeback</link>
      <description><![CDATA[伊朗石油生产不受美国多年制裁的影响，几乎恢复满负荷生产——但随着与以色列的紧张局势加剧，这种供应形势看起来变得越来越脆弱。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-10-04/mideast-s-rising-war-risk-puts-spotlight-on-iran-s-quiet-oil-comeback</guid>
      <pubDate>Fri, 04 Oct 2024 09:08:05 GMT</pubDate>
